nodes.title: Note: KSampler settings
widgets_values:
You can test and find the best setting by yourself. The following table is for reference.

| Model            | Steps | CFG |
|---------------------|---------------|---------------|
| Offical             | 50               | 4.0               
| fp8_e4m3fn             | 20                | 2.5               |
| fp8_e4m3fn + 4steps LoRA    | 4               | 1.0               |

if you want to  generate NSFW content online with Runninghub. disable the Save Image Node and the image compare node ,enable this group and link the image output to this Image To Base64 node. run the workflow. the image result will be in the show any node.

triple click the text to select and Copy all the text shown in the Show Any node to the following site to decode the image.

如果您想使用 Runninghub 在线生成 NSFW 内容，请禁用“保存图像”节点 和图像对比节点，启用此组，并将图像输出链接到此“Image to Base64”节点。再运行工作流。图片结果会以文字显示咋show any 节点。

三次单击文本以选择并将“show any”节点中显示的所有文本复制到以下站点以解码图像。

https://base64.guru/converter/decode/image
Photography, A young woman wearing lingerie, sitting on a bed in a bedroom.
